reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars A Solid Performer for Car Detailing: Detailing Brush Review
reviews.reviewText: I recently acquired a detailing brush for my car, and I'm pleased to report that it's a reliable tool for keeping my vehicle looking clean and well-maintained. This detailing brush, while not exceptional, is decently made and gets the job done effectively.One of the standout qualities of this detailing brush is its ability to reach into crevices and tight spaces. The slim, fine bristles make it easy to access areas that are often overlooked during regular cleaning, such as air vents, dashboard seams, and intricate areas around the console. This is a significant advantage for car enthusiasts who want their vehicles to be spotless inside and out.The brush also does an excellent job at dusting and removing debris from various surfaces. Whether it's the dashboard, door panels, or even the upholstery, it manages to capture and lift away dust and dirt efficiently. The bristles are sturdy enough to provide a satisfying scrub without causing any damage to the surfaces being cleaned.While this detailing brush serves its purpose well, it doesn't necessarily stand out as an exceptional product. It's a reliable tool for everyday car cleaning, but it lacks any extraordinary features or innovations. However, for those seeking a straightforward, dependable tool for maintaining their vehicle's interior, it's a good choice.In summary, this detailing brush is a solid performer that lives up to its intended purpose. It effectively cleans and dusts various surfaces in your car and excels at reaching those challenging crevices. While it may not boast any remarkable features, it's a dependable and well-made tool for car enthusiasts and anyone looking to keep their vehicle in top condition.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A complete kit for keeping your car clean
reviews.reviewText: The first kit was defective but customer service was prompt and shipped a replacement very quickly. There are 13 items in this kit and all of them are of a good quality and do help to keep the car spotless both inside and out. Most of these are standard cleaning tools that I have used but the two that standout are the air conditioner vent cleaner and the telescopic squeegee to clean the rear view mirrors when you are seated inside the vehicle. also included is the carrying bag so that all tools stay together and can be packed away in the trunk so you can also clean your car while you are traveling away from home. The Jerbor is a very good an complete kit and I will be using all of these tools to make sure my car will always look good.
